{"tid":1007021,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"疑遭愛黨中國人檢舉 女畫家反習作品在美國被下架","createTime":"2019-02-03T12:41:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-03T13:42:54.000Z","uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3f2e4f4dedf7778314e4b9268c42a783735f803d","tid":1007021,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T12:41:48.000Z","msg":"中國旅美畫家翁冰日前在美國北卡羅來納州舉行個人畫展，其中3幅「反抗習近平暴政」的畫作遭主辦方撤除。主辦單位稱因這3件作品有「政治傾向」，「有人」出來抗議，翁冰不排除是「愛黨中國人」向主辦方抗議導致作品被撤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpuSj2L6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpuSj2L6.jpg&h=3079ac39&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">中國旅美畫家翁冰的反習畫</span></div><br />\n<br />\n《自由亞洲電台》報導，翁冰這次的畫展中共展出38幅畫作，其中包括3幅與其它唯美風格迥異的作品，都是以抗議中國國家主席習近平暴政為主題，其中一幅是被潑墨的習近平畫像，這3幅作品在1月22日被主辦單位撤下。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpe4dIuk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpe4dIuk.jpg&h=c8da4a93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">翁冰所畫的被潑墨的習近平畫像。</span></div><br />\n<br />\n報導提到，主辦單位為北卡羅來納州的卡瑞老人活動中心（Cary Senior Center），工作人員雖然承認撤除翁冰的畫作，但迴避對畫作本身的評價，指撤除並非由於「政治原因」和「政治審查」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2691312\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2691312&d=GmsUkepvXW4IpX0DHJvToLHKdwoo7KeUephkEgg9e70%3D&h=49afd8de\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2691312&h=dd42cf0c\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2691312</a>"},{"pid":"4211fe8681646c97790ecd01bab755fcbb9ad47f","tid":1007021,"uid":1886,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T12:42:22.000Z","msg":"翁冰表示，主辦單位負責人回應說其畫作具有「政治傾向」，並「有人」對其畫作抗議。翁冰和一些旅美評論人士懷疑，有在美國的「親共華人」搗亂，同時認為主辦方有自我審查嫌疑，翁冰擔憂美國的言論自由正被侵蝕。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpuVuNh8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpuVuNh8.jpg&h=b3364faf&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n中國旅美畫家翁冰主張把畫筆當武器，來向中國共產黨宣戰，旨在推翻以習近平為首的獨裁政府，為中國人民爭得人權、自由和民主。"},{"pid":"9e9cde8d4c46226d1baf13c3a2c7384206791563","tid":1007021,"uid":3302,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T12:43:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 烈士"},{"pid":"e70feabbb9a6dafaff766666ddbfb9cb19de54ea","tid":1007021,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T13:28:51.000Z","msg":"中國旅美畫家翁冰主張把畫筆當武器，來向中國共產黨宣戰，旨在推翻以習近平為首的獨裁政府，為中國人民爭得人權、自由和民主。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n和理非思維<br />\n以為用筆就可以推翻中共<br />\n咁泛民一早爭取到香港民主啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad012f0a7b48838388d841571c28803375c627cf","tid":1007021,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T13:35:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"597f18b09c67a2165e2b4b9af8a42e405ddbc174","tid":1007021,"uid":229789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T13:42:16.000Z","msg":"邊個負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4db00f8e474b46c8635fbc2f0fa3848d849276d1","tid":1007021,"uid":160147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T13:42:54.000Z","msg":"自甘墜落<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}